WEBVTT

00:02.570 --> 00:05.323
- Previously on Hannibal...
- Garrett Jacob Hobbs

00:05.370 --> 00:07.065
didn't kill Cassie Boyle.
- I know.

00:07.100 --> 00:09.204
- Dad? It's for you.

00:09.240 --> 00:11.231
- I believe the as yet
unidentified caller

00:11.270 --> 00:12.498
was our copycat killer.

00:14.680 --> 00:18.639
- I wanna go home. You do this
a lot? Go places and think
about killing?

00:18.680 --> 00:20.272
- Too often.

00:20.320 --> 00:22.117
- Abigail!
(screaming)

00:22.150 --> 00:23.788
- I didn't kill that girl...

00:23.820 --> 00:26.812
- This is not self-defence,
Abigail. You butchered him.

00:26.860 --> 00:30.159
- You're the one
who called the house.
- If I keep your secret...

00:30.190 --> 00:31.452
- Then I'll keep yours.

00:36.770 --> 00:40.228
- Sometimes, at night,

00:40.270 --> 00:42.306
I leave the lights on

00:42.340 --> 00:44.661
in my little house

00:44.710 --> 00:48.305
and walk across
the flat fields...

00:48.340 --> 00:51.844
And when I look back
from a distance,

00:51.880 --> 00:54.610
the house is like
a boat on the sea.

00:57.490 --> 01:00.516
It's really the only time
I feel safe.

01:03.190 --> 01:06.091
- You stood in
the breathing silence of
Garrett Jacob Hobbs's home.

01:06.130 --> 01:08.849
The very spaces
he moved through.

01:08.900 --> 01:12.666
Tell me, Will...
Did they speak to you?

01:15.500 --> 01:18.867
- Noise and clarity.

01:18.910 --> 01:20.878
- You could sense his madness.

01:20.910 --> 01:22.878
Like a bloodhound.

01:22.910 --> 01:26.710
- I tried so hard to know
Garrett Jacob Hobbs.

01:26.750 --> 01:29.116
- No, no, no!

01:29.150 --> 01:31.516
- To see him.

01:31.550 --> 01:33.689
Garrett Jacob Hobbs, FBI!

01:35.520 --> 01:36.851
(gunshot)

01:36.890 --> 01:41.793
Past the slides and vials,

01:41.830 --> 01:44.264
beyond the lines
of the police reports,

01:44.300 --> 01:48.236
between the pixels
of all those...

01:48.270 --> 01:50.306
printed faces

01:50.340 --> 01:52.774
of sad, dead girls.

01:55.510 --> 01:57.671
- See...

02:00.220 --> 02:03.144
- How did you feel
seeing Melissa Shule,

02:03.190 --> 02:05.181
