02:11.860 --> 02:13.828
- Guilty.

02:13.860 --> 02:15.828
- Because you couldn't save her?

02:15.860 --> 02:19.637
- Because I felt
like I killed her.

02:22.810 --> 02:27.531
I got so close to him...

02:27.580 --> 02:30.469
Sometimes, I felt like

02:30.510 --> 02:33.240
we were doing the same things
at different times of day.

02:33.280 --> 02:35.441
Like I was eating

02:35.480 --> 02:38.313
or showering or sleeping
at the same time he was.

02:38.350 --> 02:41.285
- Even after he was dead?

02:42.890 --> 02:45.688
- Yeah, even after he was dead.

02:45.730 --> 02:49.461
- Like... you were becoming him.

02:49.500 --> 02:53.288
- I know who I am.

02:53.340 --> 02:55.729
